{"tid":1241593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"刷副本前綫有感","createTime":"2019-06-18T18:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:45.000Z","uid":25264,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc95cce719a6d8fbb9c0d41926f45a24efac4bb","tid":1241593,"uid":25264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"就算肯帶你地打副有鳩用咩，先唔講咩篤灰割蓆。<br />\n用埋啲濕鳩頭盔眼罩遮，二三排又易散，一係就rambo上身衝到上哂頭唔識收。<br />\n叫撚左話轉套靚啲既裝，五年後見撚到你地出到黎又係去返新手村出黎咁撚樣，你想我地點啫咁多位大帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80500b23a091463ea90936a29083e870ba5fc78","tid":1241593,"uid":25264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:26:06.000Z","msg":"唔係話想屌你地，但係我話比你地知你地個邏輯係真係錯鳩哂，有乜理由二到六排都夠膽死開遮<br />\n走佬就個個爭住衝去後，向前就搵前面條當盾推，你教返我喇不如，衝條撚咩撚"},{"pid":"ef0c12d8be4d77fe180eac6b45fc052c627819be","tid":1241593,"uid":25264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"係真係冇人會認真檢討下同實行嗰下好野喎你地"},{"pid":"6b063bfe174a53566ee4c39548ec53599cf272b6","tid":1241593,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:08:54.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"43a4e0d1e6773da7e1e98f8a7fa1d0ae544532c5","tid":1241593,"uid":25264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:17:46.000Z","msg":"係到想提下各位一齊上前既兄弟，記得要有一套自己既裝，係得你知你自己需要啲咩裝，唔好再用安全帽，n95同3m眼罩，呢套野係會累死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別強烈建議大家買3m 3200豬嘴，因為當日小弟發夢嗰陣係靠佢先可以係煲底頂到去中信大廈<br />\n仲有就係遮呢樣真係冇乜用，唔好一黎就開，由其係第三排打後，遮哂成個視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到大家知要退既時候已經太遲<br />\n個腦唔好幻想有咩陣式就可以衝得贏守得到，我地冇人受過訓練，都冇時間比我地排，根本一有咩風吹草動，二排打後已經退到去5m之後，但求大家係有組織咁後退已經係超賠率<br />\n最後就係捉實你前面嗰位朋友既腰帶/背囊，而唔係一衝就當人係盾咁死推，一走就放手向後搏命走，你一個捉實既動作已經可以救返好多位前線既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d0dd5d2ad9a2537acaf1d3ba6025ff5ca43d1c","tid":1241593,"uid":13078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:49:54.000Z","msg":"講得好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278a6c5a75959e8e346eab686cecaa81c70bb3a1","tid":1241593,"uid":149041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"最斃係就算整盾牌嗰啲 未入到去已經俾人周返出嚟"},{"pid":"22c26311baa10c850f191de75e8db00a0a6c8926","tid":1241593,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7d62779111f437a63f02c399711dd02f78fcc8","tid":1241593,"uid":195601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"唔係頭兩排都開遮真係唔多好...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}